        <q>¿Qué observan? ¿Qué se preguntan?</q>  (Students may notice: Both groups of dots are arranged as arrays. They both have 10 dots. One array has groups of 2. One array has groups of 5. Students may wonder: Why are the dots grouped differently? Are the arrays the same?)
